column5: I always see a lot of posts with stories of fishing trips to some pretty impressive looking lodges and cabins etc.  Here is the kinda place I can relate to though:     Note the finer things in life that they have to make you all feel warm and comfy during your stay
looks like a good place except that it seems there is flesh eating bacteria
pictures of the nude chicks in the background?

I like the fly catcher - the location is PERFECT.
That sir,is the perfect hunting cabin if I ever seen one. Is that fried tater slices I see there? Nothing like good friends ,food and sport.
